GOOD TIDINGS The winter winds blow with the force of a thousand demon horrors and the nobles of the Great Empire seek good tidings to lift their spirits. But worry not, as these frozen Kings and Queens can look forward to a number of exciting optimizations designed to warm their hearts and improve the playing experience of castle lords throughout the lands. These include adjustments to the royal quests, level 81 robber barons, gem package prizes, and much more!
